description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Plezier purrs with a rating of 43, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 215, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70435-22164-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [215 Votes, Top 5% Score]
